     <P style="float: left;padding: 0px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;"> The curriculum of the Programme is designed to expose the candidates to foundations of business management and deep skills in analytics.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="underlinetext">
     <P style="float: left;padding: 0px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">The courses are a judicious mix of domain knowledge, quantitative subjects, technical skills and applications. The first few modules of the Programme will focus on the domain competency along with exposure to rigors of the analytical tools and techniques. Subsequently, the participants will be given expertise in handling large data sets in terms of processing, managing, analyzing and representing them in a format that makes Business decisions easy. The latter portion of the curriculum focuses on specific problems encountered in domains such as Finance, marketing, Web, Health, Energy, Telecom etc, and candidates will learn the Business Analytics approaches to solve these problems. </p>
