     <P style="float: left;padding: 10px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;"><b>Hands on exposure:</b> Every module will entail practical assignments that complement the conceptual learning that the candidates would have gathered. These assignments will expose the candidates to solving real world business problems using tools such as SAS, R, Tableau, etc.</p>
