     <P style="float: left;padding: 10px 15px;width: 95%;margin-bottom:10px;text-align: justify;"><b>Industry project</b> is a critical component of the curriculum wherein every candidate will work on an actual industry case study. This project will act as an industry application of the learning derived from the course and will need to be presented to the faculty board for successful completion of the course. </p></div>
     


